text: Sofia Skog (born 1 October 1988) is a Swedish footballer who last played for Kopparbergs/Göteborg FC in the fully professional Damallsvenskan, the top Swedish women's league, as a midfielder. Skog played for Jitex BK from 2010 to 2013, where she scored four goals in 76 appearances. ==References== ==External links== * (archive) * (archive) * Category:1988 births Category:Swedish women's footballers Category:Living people Category:Kopparbergs/Göteborg FC players Category:Jitex BK players Category:Damallsvenskan players Category:Women's association football midfielders
